<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #222;">
    <p>Dear {{data.tlName}},</p>
    <p>
        The costing of the Tender
        {{data.tender_name}}, has been done and submitted for your approval. I have prepared the tender documents with the best of my understanding of the technical documents, the
        scope of work and the quotations received from the vendor.
    </p>
    <p>Please review the cost and approve it.</p>
    <p>
        Link:
        <a href="{{data.costingSheetLink}}">Costing sheet</a>
    </p>

    <p><strong>Tender Value (GST Inclusive):</strong> {{data.tenderValue}}</p>

    <table width="100%" cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0"
        style="border: 1px solid #444; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th style="border: 1px solid #444; background-color: #2c3e50; color: #fff; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">#</th>
                <th style="border: 1px solid #444; background-color: #2c3e50; color: #fff; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">Final Price (GST Incl.)</th>
                <th style="border: 1px solid #444; background-color: #2c3e50; color: #fff; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">Receipt (Pre GST)</th>
                <th style="border: 1px solid #444; background-color: #2c3e50; color: #fff; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">Budget (Pre GST)</th>
                <th style="border: 1px solid #444; background-color: #2c3e50; color: #fff; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">Gross Margin %</th>
                <th style="border: 1px solid #444; background-color: #2c3e50; color: #fff; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">Remarks</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {{#each data.details}}
            <tr>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{this.index}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{this.finalPrice}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{this.receipt}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{this.budget}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{this.grossMargin}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{this.remarks}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
            <tr style="background-color: #e8e8e8; font-weight: bold;">
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">Total</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{data.totalFinalPrice}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{data.totalReceipt}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{data.totalBudget}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">—</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">—</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <p>The tender due date and time is {{data.dueDate}}, {{data.dueTime}}. Please approve at least 48 hours before the tender due date and time.</p>

    <p>Best Regards,</p>
    <p>{{data.teName}}</p>
</div>